## Brave Search API 配置
- 正确路径：`openclaw.json` → `tools.web.search.provider` + `tools.web.search.apiKey`
- 错误路径 `tools.web.braveApiKey` 会导致 Gateway 启动失败（Unrecognized key）
- 文档：`openclaw/docs/brave-search.md`

